{"componentChunkName":"component---src-layouts-blog-post-layout-js","path":"/blog/debut-theme-how-to-remove-button-hover-animation","result":{"pageContext":{"id":662,"date":"2021-04-05T05:12:29","date_gmt":"2021-04-05T05:12:29","guid":{"rendered":"https://www.ezfy.club/?p=662"},"modified":"2021-04-05T05:36:17","modified_gmt":"2021-04-05T05:36:17","slug":"debut-theme-how-to-remove-button-hover-animation","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https://www.ezfy.club/debut-theme-how-to-remove-button-hover-animation/","title":{"rendered":"Debut Theme: how to remove button hover animation"},"content":{"rendered":"\n<p>On the Debut theme, whenever you hover over a button you can notice the button changes color. Depending on the type of design you&#8217;re going after this can be more of a hindrance than a bonus, so I&#8217;ll teach you how to get rid of it.</p>\n\n\n\n<h3>Adding the code to your theme</h3>\n\n\n\n<ol><li>In your Shopify admin, navigate to&nbsp;<strong>Online Store</strong>&nbsp;&gt;&nbsp;<strong>Themes&nbsp;</strong>&gt;&nbsp;<strong>Actions&nbsp;</strong>&gt;&nbsp;<strong>Edit Code</strong>.<br><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1349\" height=\"614\" class=\"wp-image-626\" style=\"width: 600px;\" src=\"https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/edit-code.jpg\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/edit-code.jpg 1349w, https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/edit-code-600x273.jpg 600w, https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/edit-code-1200x546.jpg 1200w, https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/edit-code-768x350.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1349px) 100vw, 1349px\" /><br></li><li>Find a file called <strong>theme.liquid</strong>.</li><li>In your <strong>theme.liquid file</strong>, find the <em>&lt;/body&gt;</em> <em>(press CTRL + F or command + F on Mac)</em></li><li>Paste this code right above the <em>&lt;/body&gt;</em> tag <a rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" href=\"https://gist.github.com/dpw1/720f4f3968dfbc5720eed0b5f1bc6840\" target=\"_blank\">(click here to grab the code)</a></li><li>Save the file and you&#8217;re ready to go.</li></ol>\n\n\n\n<h3>What to do if it&#8217;s showing a different color instead of removing hover</h3>\n\n\n\n<p>By default, all buttons hover animations need a background color. This code will automatically use the original button&#8217;s color (or whichever color you chose on the Debut customize page). <br><br>However, on earlier versions of the Debut theme it may fail to automatically pick the original button&#8217;s color and you&#8217;ll need to set it manually. Simply replace the <strong>#3a3a3a</strong> in the code with your button&#8217;s default HEX color.</p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\">\n<div class=\"wp-block-group\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\">\n<div class=\"wp-block-group\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\"></div></div>\n</div></div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\">\n<h3>You may also like</h3>\n\n\n\n<p>Using the Debut theme? Make your store stand out of the crowd with our other tutorials:</p>\n\n\n\n<ul><li><a rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" href=\"https://ezfycode.com/blog/debut-shopify-theme-how-to-add-swipe-for-product-page-images\" target=\"_blank\">Add swipe/arrows to your product page images</a></li><li><a rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" href=\"https://ezfycode.com/blog/debut-theme-sticky-navigation-bar-tutorial\" target=\"_blank\">Sticky navigation bar (plus 20+ customizable features)</a></li><li><a rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" href=\"https://ezfycode.com/blog/show-second-image-on-hover-debut-theme\" data-type=\"URL\" data-id=\"https://ezfycode.com/blog/show-second-image-on-hover-debut-theme\" target=\"_blank\">Show second image on hover</a></li></ul>\n\n\n\n<p></p>\n</div></div>\n</div></div>\n\n\n\n<p></p>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>Remove the hover animation for buttons on your Debut theme.</p>\n","protected":false},"author":1,"featured_media":666,"comment_status":"open","ping_status":"open","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":[],"categories":[9],"tags":[154,157],"image_alt":"","acf":[],"featured_image_src":"https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2021/04/Debut-Slider-Pro-10-600x338.png","featured_image_small_src":"https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2021/04/Debut-Slider-Pro-10-100x100.png","post_count":0,"categories_names":["Blog"],"tag_names":["Code Tutorial","debut theme"],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https://www.ezfy.club/json/wp/v2/posts/662"}],"collection":[{"href":"https://www.ezfy.club/json/wp/v2/posts"}],"about":[{"href":"https://www.ezfy.club/json/wp/v2/types/post"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https://www.ezfy.club/json/wp/v2/users/1"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https://www.ezfy.club/json/wp/v2/comments?post=662"}],"version-history":[{"count":4,"href":"https://www.ezfy.club/json/wp/v2/posts/662/revisions"}],"predecessor-version":[{"id":672,"href":"https://www.ezfy.club/json/wp/v2/posts/662/revisions/672"}],"wp:featuredmedia":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https://www.ezfy.club/json/wp/v2/media/666"}],"wp:attachment":[{"href":"https://www.ezfy.club/json/wp/v2/media?parent=662"}],"wp:term":[{"taxonomy":"category","embeddable":true,"href":"https://www.ezfy.club/json/wp/v2/categories?post=662"},{"taxonomy":"post_tag","embeddable":true,"href":"https://www.ezfy.club/json/wp/v2/tags?post=662"}],"curies":[{"name":"wp","href":"https://api.w.org/{rel}","templated":true}]}}},"staticQueryHashes":["1739988571","1995349551"]}